phase2.explanation:
🤖 **Common bottom navigation mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| No Scaffold | Wrap in Scaffold |
| No NavHost | Add NavHost |
| No state saving | Use saveState and restoreState |
| Too many items | Limit to 5 items |
| No selected state | Track current route |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
// 1. Use Scaffold
Scaffold(
    bottomBar = { NavigationBar { ... } }
) { innerPadding ->
    NavHost(modifier = Modifier.padding(innerPadding)) { ... }
}

// 2. Track selected state
val currentRoute = navController.currentBackStackEntry?.destination?.route
selected = currentRoute == screen.route

// 3. Use popUpTo
navController.navigate(screen.route) {
    popUpTo(navController.graph.findStartDestination().id) {
        saveState = true
    }
    launchSingleTop = true
    restoreState = true
}

// 4. Limit to 5 items
val items = listOf(Home, Search, Profile, Settings)  // 4 items
```

